description: This Chainlink VRF top 15% score Anurak purrs with a rating of 66, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 132, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, Stringalong for East, Nine Lives for South, and Nine Lives for West. Anurak has the personality suit of hodler. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/20662-77993-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Anurak [132 Votes, Top 15% Score]
